high_descs: Turn around and walk to the shelves.

Turn around, go straight then a right to the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the mug inside for a little bit and then take it out.
Turn around, take a left and take the mug back to the shelves.
Set the mug on the shelves.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the shelves in the corner behind you.

Chill the mug inside of the fridge.
Turn around, and go around the kitchen island to return to the shelf.
Put the mug on the second shelf, to the left of the glass.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled mug on the shelf.

Carry the cup to the fridge and put it in the fridge
Take the cup out of the fridge
